flowchart TB
    Maintainer([Maintainer]) --> CLI[generate_architecture_candidate CLI]
    CLI --> LocalGate{Loopback LM Studio endpoint?}
    LocalGate -->|no| RejectRemote[Reject remote provider]
    LocalGate -->|yes| ContextGuard[Explicit context allowlist<br/>path, type, count, and size limits]

    ContextGuard --> Canonical[(Registered canonical .mmd<br/>read-only exemplar)]
    ContextGuard --> Source[Explicit repository source files]
    ContextGuard -->|traversal, secrets, or unsupported file| RejectContext[Reject context]
    Canonical --> Normalize[Normalize legacy HTML line breaks<br/>for strict prompt evidence]
    Normalize --> CandidateService[ArchitectureCandidateService]
    Source --> CandidateService
    Request[Maintainer change request<br/>plus required visible labels] --> CandidateService

    CandidateService --> Agent[DiagramAgent]
    Agent --> Graph[LangGraph generate_diagram node]
    Graph --> Provider[LLMDiagramProvider]
    Provider --> Gemma[Local LM Studio Gemma]
    Gemma --> Validate[Passive Mermaid validator<br/>type, size, lines, and active-content rejection]
    Validate --> Labels{Required labels present?}
    Labels -->|no; once| Correction[Bounded semantic correction<br/>previous source plus missing labels]
    Correction --> Agent
    Labels -->|no after retry| RejectCandidate[Reject candidate]
    Labels -->|yes| OutputGuard{New .candidate.mmd path?}

    OutputGuard -->|canonical or existing path| RejectOutput[Reject output]
    OutputGuard -->|new review path| CandidateMMD[(Candidate Mermaid source)]
    CandidateMMD --> Renderer[Pinned Mermaid CLI<br/>Chromium render]
    Renderer --> CandidateSVG[(Candidate SVG)]
    CandidateMMD --> Review[Technical and visual review]
    CandidateSVG --> Review
    Review -->|approved manual edit or promotion| Updated[(Reviewed canonical .mmd and SVG)]
    Review -->|rejected| Revise[Revise evidence or request<br/>and run the command again]

    Protection[No automatic canonical overwrite<br/>no persistence or hardware authority]
    CandidateService -.-> Protection

